# Goal: Build a Notion-Style Rich Text Editor

The objective is to replace the basic text area with a full-featured, modular, Notion-like editor using **Tiptap**. We will architect this so the code is easy to read, heavily commented, and highly modular (great for learning).

## User Review Required

